title: It's a Big Freaking Cookie
description: Cameo Who Costs More?, Dave gives Jenny trivia questions and if she gets them wrong she has to drink something she can't see what it is, Lauren tells us what happened after she told HR about the photos on her co-workers computer and it's not what we thought, War of the Roses, the Monster Cookie debate, and more!
